description:
The first file of this supplement contains the data extraction protocol and the list of included articles, with corresponding access links (article DOIs, OER references, and related resources) from the systematic review on FAIR OERs.  
  The second file contains the search query used for the literature review (MEDLINE, WoS, IEEE Xplore, ACM Digital Library).  
 &nbsp;

